  </Speakers>
  <Strings>
    <Section>Main Text</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>アビス、アビス、アビス！！
実は俺さま、アビスこそが
本命だったのよね</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Abyss, Abyss, Abyss!!
Truth is, Abyss was my favorite the whole time.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>11</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>そうなのか？
なんでそんなにアビスがいいんだよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Oh yeah?
Why do you like Abyss so much?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>10</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>だってさ、アビスのヒロインって
めっちゃ可愛いメロンな娘なのよ？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>'Cause I mean, Abyss' heroine is the
super cute melons girl, you know?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>11</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>やっぱりそういう理由か</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>So that's all it's acually about in the end.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>10</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>まぁいいや。
俺も全力で応援するから
今度こそ決めようぜ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Well, whatever. I'll be supporting you with
everything I've got, so get out there and settle this!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>10</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
